{"tid":1323613,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我宣佈！【與警賊切割運動】正式開始！！","createTime":"2019-07-16T09:54:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T09:00:56.000Z","uid":168703,"like":286,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":60,"replies":[{"pid":"73327ad8b448a1e3c8ad926429bc1c7d4bce8134","tid":1323613,"uid":168703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T09:54:24.000Z","msg":"警賊嘅惡行唔多講，打人打得咁爽唔係諗住除低制服可以過番人類嘅生活呀嘛？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n學689話齋！恥與為伍呀！<br />\n所以，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">【與警賊切割運動】，正式開始！</span></span><br />\n同狗隻來往，簡直係你人生嘅污點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n為咗阻止瘋狗症傳播，你需要及早同警賊<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">斷絕來往！</span></span><br />\n由今日起，我地要從生活上所有事情，對警賊進行杯葛！<br />\n聽落好似好小學雞，但其實咁樣先可以懲罰佢地，為自己著制服時嘅所作所為負責<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n行動形式有好多種，包括：絕交、分手、unfriend、unfollow、唔做佢生意、俾綠帽佢戴等等<br />\n<br />\n例子一: 最近身邊如果有狗隻會擺酒，可以選擇人同禮都唔到，並且絕交！<br />\n例子二: 足球隊籃球隊可選擇唔再俾狗隻參與，另開新group/隊<br />\n例子三: 直接同狗隻講，因為你係狗，所以俾帽你戴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mye2t7A.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fmye2t7A.png&h=be579697&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n從今日起，#UNFRIENDPOLICE"},{"pid":"ad3ff8b883d0edbd9dd02b99407e91c2243e9788","tid":1323613,"uid":168703,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T09:54:48.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"3f57dfa35ece5ba91bb78554e1c3fd67aefe87a5","tid":1323613,"uid":168703,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T09:55:14.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"6b069b8af49e0f2851f4ba22ce7d6bde33d010db","tid":1323613,"uid":280547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T09:56:23.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"d090898025998fbcbe1d59e9de4f9faa107ff65c","tid":1323613,"uid":31381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0